casebody.data:
James P. MANNING
v.
ROSE HILL GOLF CLUB, INC. No. 2017-177-Appeal (WB 14-532) Supreme Court of Rhode Island. December 14, 2018 For Plaintiff: Stephen F. Del Sesto, Esq. For Defendant: Robert E. Flaherty, Esq. Present: Suttell, C.J.,Goldberg, Robinson, and Indeglia, JJ.

ORDER

The Court being evenly divided, the judgment of the Superior Court is affirmed.

Justice Flaherty did not participate.
